Class Album

java.lang.Object
model.Album
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Album extends Object implements Serializable
The Album class represents a photo album that contains a collection of photos. It provides functionality to manage photos, retrieve album details, and determine the earliest and latest dates of the photos in the album.

This class implements Serializable to allow serialization of album objects.

Features of the Album class include:

  • Adding and removing photos
  • Retrieving the total number of photos
  • Getting the earliest and latest dates of photos
